data.description: Thousands under tax value!! Great opportunity to get into Rock House Cove community. With a private setting and the ability to have views from the upper part of the property or build towards the bottom which is more level gives you multiple options. HOA is only $200 annually so there is no rush to build as well. Being under 9K per acre this gives you the price to own a sizeable piece of land at a great value. Come build you mountain retreat and let the relaxation begin. For the best lay of the land please use the "Land Glide" app.
